<h3>About Application Tracker</h3>

<p>Welcome to the Application Tracker! A cross-platform tool to help you keep track of your job applications in an organized and efficient manner.</p>

<h4>Features</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Track the status of your job applications</li>
    <li>Set reminders for follow-ups</li>
    <li>Store contact information for recruiters</li>
</ul>

<h4>Why I Made It</h4>
<p>I created the Application Tracker to streamline the job application process. Keeping track of multiple applications can be overwhelming, and I wanted to build a tool that simplifies this task and helps job seekers stay organized and focused.</p>